data.description: Beautiful Venetian Isles Pool Home On Wide Sailboat Canal.  Spacious Open Floor Plan With A Split Bedroom Plan.  3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms & Over 1,700 SF Of Living Area.  Light & Airy With A Modern Coastal Feel.  Porcelain Tile Flooring In Main Living Areas.  Rich Engineered Wood Plank Flooring In All Bedrooms.  Incredible Kitchen Offers Wood Cabinetry With Ample Storage.  Stainless Steel Appliances Are 1-2 Years Old,  Granite Counter-Tops & Breakfast Bar.  Built-In Desk Off Kitchen & Dining Area.  Gracious Sized Master Suite With A Gorgeous Master Bathroom With Walk-in Shower & Leathered Granite Counter-Tops.  Dining Area Overlooks Inground Pool, Lanai & Waterway.  Tropical Back Yard With Saltillo Tiled Pool Deck, Coconut & Royal Palm Trees.  Upgraded Seawall, Composite Dock, 13k Lb Boat Lift and An Underwater Fish Light.  Deep Water Access To Open Tampa Bay & The Gulf Of Mexico.  Most Windows & 2-Car Garage Door Are Impact Rated.  Andersen Certified Energy Star Insulated Dining Room Windows & Patio Doors.  Plantation Shutters, Upgraded Electric Panel & More.  Truly Florida Living At It's Finest!
